name: Black Widow Eat My Soul
description:
I was so excited when Kim took the train and Berlin and let me photograph her.  We had been chatting online for quite some time and it was a dream to have her wear my costumes and grace my camera lense.  Never have I seen such an exquisite dark seductress as her!  She is impossibly beautiful and a talented makeup artist and self portrait artist.  She's also a little evil, which I like in a woman!  I hope you enjoy staring into her eyes as much as I do! 

Model is Kim www.instagram.com/justcallmekim_makeup/
Headdress and photography by BubblesAndFrown.etsy.com
Waist cincher and collar by Tommy Vowles https://www.instagram.com/tommyvowles/

This whole outfit is made with vegan materials, if that kinda stuff makes you happy!
